request.description:
Import addresses from a JSON file and verify them using the provided password. The endpoint will:
1. Verify existing addresses in the database using the password
2. Verify addresses in the imported file
3. Import new addresses (skipping duplicates)

File format example:
{
    "addresses": [
        {
            "address": "solana_address_here",
            "private_key": "encrypted_private_key_here"
        }
    ]
}

